{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0123uvGanCxArFGDUFWLxAmQ","type":"tool_result","content":"commit 0c9112f4d34135ccbc68d47d910fb3c788b6fd9c\nAuthor: lucas <lucas@perfectlunacy.com>\nDate:   Mon Mar 2 13:00:18 2026 -0800\n\n    feat: migrate project layout from cloche/ to .cloche/ subdirectory\n    \n    Existing projects can now use Cloche without restructuring their files.\n    Cloche-specific files (Dockerfile, workflows, prompts) live in .cloche/\n    at the project root. The container gets the full project source copied in,\n    with optional override files from .cloche/overrides/ applied on top.\n    \n    Key changes:\n    - Docker runtime copies entire project root instead of cloche/ subdir\n    - .cloche/overrides/ mechanism for container-specific file overrides\n    - All path references updated: CLI, daemon, local runtime, evolution\n    - cloche init scaffolds .cloche/ with prompts/ and overrides/ dirs\n    - Documentation updated (CLAUDE.md, USAGE.md, workflows.md)\n    - All tests updated and passing\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\ndiff --git a/.beads/issues.jsonl b/.beads/issues.jsonl\nindex b3de350..f0bb60f 100644\n--- a/.beads/issues.jsonl\n+++ b/.beads/issues.jsonl\n@@ -56,12 +56,12 @@\n {\"id\":\"cloche-oa5\",\"title\":\"Prompt Curator (Branch A)\",\"description\":\"ACE-style prompt curation: merge lessons as structured bullets, dedup, snapshot pre-change state. See Task 12 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.778505766-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:03:14.113618634-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:03:14.113618634-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-oa5\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-osk\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.918535374-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-osk\",\"title\":\"Evolution Reflector stage\",\"description\":\"ACE-style lesson extraction from execution traces. Structured lessons with confidence levels. See Task 11 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.739151519-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.529265221-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.529265221-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-osk\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-0aa\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.884318161-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-q6n\",\"title\":\"Update Run model for concurrent steps\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.717730563-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n-{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"title\":\"Subdirectory layout, daemon-side extraction, and poll command\",\"description\":\"Move cloche project files into ./cloche/ subdirectory, replace in-container git push with daemon-side extraction via docker cp + git worktrees, and add a poll CLI command. See docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-design.md and docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-impl.md\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"epic\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:36.813893794-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:36.813893794-08:00\"}\n+{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"title\":\"Subdirectory layout, daemon-side extraction, and poll command\",\"description\":\"Move cloche project files into ./cloche/ subdirectory, replace in-container git push with daemon-side extraction via docker cp + git worktrees, and add a poll CLI command. See docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-design.md and docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-impl.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"epic\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:36.813893794-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.846404063-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.846406999-08:00\"}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"title\":\"Add BaseSHA field to domain and persistence\",\"description\":\"Add BaseSHA string field to domain.Run struct. Add ALTER TABLE migration for base_sha column in SQLite. Update CreateRun, GetRun, ListRuns, ListRunsSince to persist/read BaseSHA.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:42.907595121-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T15:39:47.752780627-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T15:39:47.752783963-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:42.909407284-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.10\",\"title\":\"Implement container liveness check in GetStatus handler\",\"description\":\"Add ContainerStatus struct and Inspect method to ContainerRuntime interface. Implement Inspect in Docker adapter using docker inspect. Add stub in local adapter. Update GetStatus handler to call Inspect and populate container_alive/container_dead_since fields.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"create